{"tid":816961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風前做好準備    精明主婦：買了4日餸","createTime":"2018-09-13T05:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T05:43:23.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b81afd4b2543f0529da3c8ae1dfd8e9406b57e6","tid":816961,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180913/large/1536814769_29c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180913%2Flarge%2F1536814769_29c1.jpg&h=8d53f7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風山竹來勢洶洶，天文台呼籲市民及早做好防風準備。家庭主婦當然為一家人的肚皮着想，今日已經張羅餸菜，塞滿手拉車。有主婦稱，菜價比往日略高。<br />\n<br />\n上午11時左右，旺角奶路臣街街市人頭湧湧，無論菜檔、肉檔和生果檔，也擠得水洩不通。麥女士稱：「買多少少囉，買多兩日。豬肉呀，放得既菜呀！」另一位主婦馮女士表示，買了兩三日的菜「怕打風呀！菜價貴咗一啲，貴兩三蚊左右。節瓜、菜心也貴了。」<br />\n<br />\n來港一年多的錢女士未雨綢繆，買了4天的餸菜。錢說：「椰子菜、蘿蔔和水果等。因為星期五六下雨，菜價會漲高。今日也馬上漲價了，幾塊錢吧！12元賣15元、10元賣12元，還能接受。」"},{"pid":"1b35da9fa6b01892d6f929a429144451317c9d57","tid":816961,"uid":29820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"手持菜心有西屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046a5803b213102e83f095c5bd90a72db7d1b580","tid":816961,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"次次打風都有呢d人，講到好似世界末日咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f666c7ae6033dfece1f96dc5077b166b8556c0f","tid":816961,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"吒個世界有凍肉的,呢d人超級誇張"},{"pid":"6deb347297ebaed6e68b91db9bf82454c532baad","tid":816961,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"買咁多煮埋隔埋屋嗰份都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45983eea8abeb3bdca3241f8ae9ce1758c6853a8","tid":816961,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"打風啲菜貴呀, 唔係有冇嘅問題"}]}